   Ames Research Center Education banner

   Welcome to the Web site for the NASA Ames Office of Education!
   We involve the educational community in our endeavors to inspire
   Americas students, create learning opportunities and enlighten
   inquisitive minds. NASA education mission statement.
   About NASA Education
   NASA uses its unique resources to support educational excellence for
   all. NASAs national education program is carried out through NASA
   Headquarters and the eleven NASA field centers (such as NASA Ames
   Research Center in northern California).
   In addition to direct contact with educators, students and the general
   public, NASA provides information, materials and services to the larger
   education community.
